  is <html:em>not</html:em> separated. Though it still have Stone fibres (cf. <fr:link href="/schm-IGER/" title="Separated maps between affine schemes have Stone fibres" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-IGER/" display-uri="schm-IGER" type="local">Remark <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-IGER/" display-uri="schm-IGER" /></fr:link>).
